<div style="background:var(--loam-white);min-height:60vh">
  <div style="background:var(--loam-black);padding:64px var(--space-6) 48px">
    <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:16px">HASSLE-FREE</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(48px,7vw,88px);color:var(--loam-white);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:.02em">Returns &amp; exchanges</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px var(--space-6);font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#E8E6E1">

    <!-- Crash replacement callout -->
    <div style="background:var(--loam-neon);padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:48px;display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:flex-start">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:56px;color:#0A0A0A;line-height:1;flex-shrink:0">40%</div>
      <div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;font-size:14px;color:#0A0A0A;margin-bottom:6px">CRASH REPLACEMENT SCHEME</p>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(0,0,0,0.75);margin-bottom:12px">Crashed and trashed your kit? We'll replace it at 40% off, no questions asked. Because crashes happen, and you shouldn't have to choose between riding and replacing your gear.</p>
        <a href="/pages/crash-replacement" style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.18em;background:var(--loam-black);color:var(--loam-neon);padding:10px 18px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block">CLAIM NOW →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:0 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">Our returns policy</h2>
    <p>We want you to love your Loam Co. kit. If something is not right, we make it easy to return or exchange within <strong>30 days of delivery</strong>.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">What we accept</h2>
    <ul style="margin-left:0;padding-left:0;list-style:none">
      <li style="padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-left:20px;position:relative"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:#DAEE01;font-weight:700">✓</span> Unworn, unwashed items with original tags attached</li>
      <li style="padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-left:20px;position:relative"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:#DAEE01;font-weight:700">✓</span> Items in original packaging (or equivalent)</li>
      <li style="padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-left:20px;position:relative"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:#DAEE01;font-weight:700">✓</span> Wrong size or colour received</li>
      <li style="padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-left:20px;position:relative"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:#DAEE01;font-weight:700">✓</span> Faulty or defective items (any time within warranty)</li>
      <li style="padding:10px 0;padding-left:20px;position:relative"><span style="position:absolute;left:0;color:#e55;">✗</span> Worn, washed, or items without tags (unless faulty)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">How to return</h2>
    <ol style="padding-left:20px">
      <li style="margin-bottom:12px">Email <a href="mailto:ride.loamco@gmail.com" style="color:#E8E6E1;font-weight:600">ride.loamco@gmail.com</a> with your order number and reason for return. We'll respond within 48 hours with a returns authorisation and address.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:12px">Package your item securely and send it back using a tracked service. UK returns: we'll send you a prepaid Royal Mail label. International returns: please use your local postal service (costs are non-refundable unless the item is faulty).</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:12px">Once received and inspected, refunds are processed within 5 working days to your original payment method. Exchanges are dispatched the same day we receive your return.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">Faulty items</h2>
    <p>If your item is faulty or has a manufacturing defect, we'll cover return postage and either replace or refund — your choice. Please email <a href="mailto:ride.loamco@gmail.com" style="color:#E8E6E1;font-weight:600">ride.loamco@gmail.com</a> with photos of the defect and your order number.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">Exchanges</h2>
    <p>Want a different size or colour? Email us before returning and we'll hold stock for you. Exchanges are dispatched with free standard delivery.</p>

  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Returns Page",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Returns Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
